---
import GlobalLayout from '../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro';
---

<GlobalLayout title="Who We Help | Families, Individuals, Professionals & Business Owners" description="We help families, individuals, professionals, and business owners move from uncertainty to clarity. Customized financial education and protection strategies.">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-amber-500/20 bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 lg:py-24">
    <!-- Background image, right-aligned -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
      style="background-image: url('/clarity-horizon.png'); background-position: right center;"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <!-- Gradient overlay matching home hero style -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 z-[1]"
      style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #1A2C46 0%, #1A2C46 45%, rgba(26,44,70,0.96) 55%, rgba(26,44,70,0.75) 68%, rgba(26,44,70,0.4) 80%, transparent 92%);"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <!-- Extra tint on small screens -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[1] bg-[#1A2C46]/60 md:bg-transparent" aria-hidden="true" />

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
          Moving From Uncertainty to <span class="text-amber-500">Clarity</span> and <span class="text-amber-500">Confidence</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          We help families from all walks of life make informed financial choices that support both today's needs and tomorrow's goals.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Who We Serve</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our specialized guidance is designed to simplify complex financial topics so you can feel informed and in control of your future.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-amber-500 flex flex-col">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/audience-family.png" alt="Family reviewing plans at a table" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8 flex-grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Families</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
              Through our "Project 500 Families" mission, we provide education, thoughtful strategy, and personalized guidance to help you build protection, flexibility, and lasting financial security.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-amber-500 flex flex-col">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/audience-individual.png" alt="Individual reading documents" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8 flex-grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Individuals</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
              We believe you deserve to understand your financial future. We empower you with financial education first, so you understand exactly how money works.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-amber-500 flex flex-col">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/audience-professional.png" alt="Professional in modern office" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8 flex-grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Professionals</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
              We design customized strategies that adapt to life's changes, ensuring you have income protection, tax-advantaged strategies, and retirement income flexibility.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-amber-500 flex flex-col">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/audience-business.png" alt="Confident business owner" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8 flex-grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Business Owners</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
              We simplify complex protection strategies to guard your assets and help you build long-term strategies designed to outpace inflation and create a lasting family legacy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-100 border-y border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Beyond Saving. Toward Strategic Protection.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Saving alone isn't enough. Many traditional advice models overlook protection and flexibility. We help you position your finances for protection, flexibility, and long-term control so you can navigate the risks most families don't see coming.
      </p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/500families-infinitewealthacademy/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold rounded-md text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-amber-600 hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
        Book a Strategy Session
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</GlobalLayout>
